These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, coffee
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, classical, jazz
1. the fan of classical is the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking coffee is between the fan of jazz and the person drinking sprite##2
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | sprite | coffee | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | classical     | country    | jazz   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, police-officer, chef
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the chef is between the videographer and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | chess    | skydiving        | magic-tricks |
| Job     | police-officer | chef | videographer         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, coffee
3 different pets are kept: rat, snake, chinchilla
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking juice is between the owner of the snake and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | lemonade | juice     | coffee |
| Pet        | snake  | chinchilla | rat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, trance, techno
3 different pets are kept: ferret, goat, cat
1. the fan of d&b is the owner of the ferret##1
2. the fan of techno is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the ferret##2
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | techno     | d&b |
| Pet           | goat | cat | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, drawing, puzzles
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, horse, rabbit
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the horse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | drawing | puzzles     | photography |
| Pet     | rabbit    | guinea-pig | horse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, chinese, american
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, cycling, sailing
1. the person who's sport is soccer is between the american and the australian##2
2. the australian is the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the chinese is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | australian  | chinese   | american        |
| Sport         | cycling | soccer | sailing |

