.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, mango, tomato
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, canadian, thai
1. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the spanish is between the person eating tomato and the canadian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | mango  | asparagus  | tomato |
| Nationality   | canadian | spanish | thai     |

