.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, musical, horror
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, french, russian
1. the person watching musical movies is the russian##1
2. the french is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching horror movies##2
3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | disaster  | musical  |
| Nationality   | pakistani | french | russian |

