.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, cycling, climbing
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, helicopter, jet-ski
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person driving the scooter is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person driving the helicopter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | climbing | water-polo | cycling  |
| Transport   | jet-ski    | scooter        | helicopter |

