.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, juice
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, cranberry, apple
1. the person eating apple is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person eating asparagus##2
2. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | hot-chocolate      | juice      |
| Food       | cranberry  | apple | asparagus |

