.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, classical, dubstep
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the fan of classical##2
3. the fan of pop is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up   | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | pop | classical   |

 